divs: Sighting DetailsGiant Diamond, I was outside watching the sky because I have seen objects up there for the past few days off and on , there was a local story in the news paper about it and no one can idnetify what the objects are, I have seen lights orbiting the exterior of the craft. I first thought it was just a star untill I looked through some binoculars and I realized I seen a flying object. I am amazed by this and I am honored to be seeing it!
